%% Data Flow Diagram - llama-stack-k8s-operator
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Reconciler
    participant KustomizeEngine as Kustomize Manifest<br/>Renderer
    participant LlamaServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 1: CR Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (CR created/updated)<br/>In-process, ServiceAccount
    Operator->>KustomizeEngine: Render manifests with plugins<br/>(NamePrefix, Namespace, FieldMutator, NetworkPolicy)
    KustomizeEngine-->>Operator: Rendered K8s resources
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, SA,<br/>PVC, NetworkPolicy, PDB, HPA,<br/>Ingress, RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 2: Health Check & Status Update

    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP plaintext, No auth
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP plaintext, No auth
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP plaintext, No auth
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Version info
    Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH CR status<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 3: ConfigMap Change Detection

    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: ConfigMap watch event<br/>In-process, ServiceAccount
    Operator->>Operator: Compute content-hash<br/>of ConfigMap data
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment annotation<br/>(config-hash change)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token
    K8sAPI->>LlamaServer: Rolling restart<br/>(annotation change triggers rollout)
